camSetFov 
Behavior: local 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Set the zoom level (field of view) of the given camera. The default 
 zoom level is 0.7, 0.01 is the nearest and 2 the furthest zoom value 
. The angle of the field of view is atan(FOV)*2 radians when in 4:3 aspect 
 ratio. Needs the call of camCommit to be conducted.  
Syntax:  
 camera camSetFov level 
Parameters: 
camera: Object - object of type "camera" 
level: Number - zoom level, range 0.01 to 2 (see description above) 
Return Value: 
 Nothing